&lt;h1 id="extrapolating-computing"&gt;Extrapolating Computing&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nov 6 2009&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Remember when mainframes did all of the computing? And workstations were dumb terminals docked to the mainframes? The terminals had less power, but were more &amp;ldquo;mobile.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Microsoft is Dead</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/microsoft/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Apr 2007 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/microsoft/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_zh/microsoft/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
